1
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,440
Thank you.

2
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,160
What is your name?

3
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,840
My name is Su Xia.

4
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,280
My name is Xiao Qi.

5
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,380
You must be hungry.

6
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:31,520
Eat.

7
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,280
Thank you.

8
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,820
You are from the Lu family?

9
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,320
Do you hate the Lu family?

10
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,960
Don't be nervous.

11
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:51,680
Because

12
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,810
I hate the Lu family too.

13
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,060
Are you scared?

14
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,560
There is no turning back
if you want revenge.

15
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,960
This path has just begun.

16
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,770
You still have a choice.

17
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:32,360
Can you forget those bad memories?

18
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,740
Can you forgive the Lu family?

19
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:47,140
No matter what choice
you make in the future,

20
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,760
I hope when you grow up,

21
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,890
you won't regret it.

22
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,640
Do me a favor.

23
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,800
Sometimes,

24
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:39,490
you have to allow yourself
to enjoy good food.

25
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,329
Enjoyment has always been a luxury for me.

26
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,920
What's wrong?

27
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,360
Fan, where are you going?

28
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,890
The guys are still waiting.

29
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,880
Su Xia, I taught you

30
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,650
to respect your opponents,

31
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,760
even if it's just acting.

32
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,600
Mr. Lu, what do you mean?

33
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,960
I'm taking her home.

34
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:12,840
The Lu family doesn't have
a rule for late-night blind dates.

35
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,800
What home?

36
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,900
Her last name is Su.

37
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,120
But she lives with the Lu family.

38
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,920
You said it yourself.

39
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,440
I don't deserve
to be a part of the Lu family,

40
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,970
so I don't have to follow
your family's rules.

41
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,660
Let go, both of you!

42
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,450
What's wrong? What's going on?

43
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,530
Fan, what are you doing?

44
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,000
They are on a blind date.

45
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,800
You date him.

46
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,280
Why would I date him?

47
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,640
Didn't you say you like him?

48
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,640
When did I say that?

49
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,640
I never said that.

50
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:35,680
Wait.

51
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,920
Mr. Xiao, don't be angry.

52
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,360
No fighting.

53
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,240
Lu Fan!

54
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,400
Lu Fan!

55
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,240
This is my car!

56
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:19,520
Mr. Xiao, Lu Fan is acting crazy.

57
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,690
Just ignore him.

58
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,440
Sir, give Mr. Qin another plate of meat.

59
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,200
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

60
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:25,930
So generous.

61
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,560
Lu Fan

62
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,960
and I

63
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,640
are childhood friends
who grew up together.

64
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,900
Look what he did today.

65
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,080
He dumped me on the side
of the road in the middle of the night

66
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,010
to go on a blind date for his sister.

67
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,720
Tell me,

68
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,080
is this a loss of humanity

69
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,159
or a decline of morals?

70
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,570
Let's not go on a blind date.

71
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,580
Let's become sworn brothers.

72
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,250
I'll break off my friendship with him.

73
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,240
Eat.

74
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,160
Well...

75
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,720
Mr. Xiao, this is raw beef, right?

76
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,440
It's raw.

77
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,820
I don't quite understand.

78
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,860
You don't understand.

79
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,060
How can we be friends if you don't?

80
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,440
Mr. Xiao,

81
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,520
it's just a plate of raw beef.

82
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,620
Don't be like this.

83
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,160
Eat.

84
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,560
Eat it up.

85
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,600
Swallow it.

86
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,720
How did it taste?

87
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,320
Bloody.

88
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,480
Barbaric.

89
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,720
Survival.

90
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:02,680
Struggle.

91
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,820
The taste of your past.

92
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,760
Mr. Xiao,

93
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:12,100
don't drown your sorrows in alcohol.

94
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,960
I never do that.

95
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,930
I did drink a bit too much today.

96
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,120
Maybe it's because I'm in a bad mood.

97
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:44,000
Don't you love drinking
with men late at night?

98
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,720
Come on.

99
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,760
Drink up!

100
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,800
What exactly do you want?

101
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,480
What do I want?

102
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,520
I've tried everything.

103
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:21,810
You're the one who wants
nothing to do with me.

104
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,040
Every time,

105
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,360
when I finally feel like
I'm getting closer to you,

106
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,610
you retreat back to where you were.

107
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,120
Do you think I don't know?

108
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,080
You went on a business trip abroad

109
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,640
for half a month

110
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,600
because you didn't want to see me.

111
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,799
You were avoiding me.

112
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:43,640
I gave up and went on a blind date.

113
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,240
Then why are you upset again?

114
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,800
It's not about what I want.

115
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,600
It's about what you want me to do.

116
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,840
I know.

117
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,200
You don't like my sister.

118
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,120
And you don't like me either.

119
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,440
Then who am I supposed to be to you,

120
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,720
Lu Fan?

121
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,760
Should I continue being your sister

122
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,840
or a total stranger?

123
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,560
I lost.

124
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,560
How about this? Let's just have a toast.

125
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,160
After this drink,

126
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,640
we're even.

127
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,080
Lu Fan!

128
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,440
You can leave.

129
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,760
Su Xia, you won.

130
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:38,960
You won.

131
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,490
Brother, have some candied hawthorn.

132
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:48,000
Su Xia, you've grown bolder.

133
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:50,360
How dare you eat something
so dirty and unsanitary?

134
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,240
Why wouldn't I?

135
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,400
I'll eat it for you to see.

136
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,560
Enough of it! Let's go home for dinner!
